data.description: 3% Fixed Rate Assumable VA loan available to eligible buyers!   Welcome to this remarkable home that offers stunning views of the majestic Sandia Mountains, West Mesa sunsets, and the captivating city lights of Albuquerque. Step onto the expansive wraparound balcony or relax on the inviting pool deck, surrounded by the ultimate luxury of the great outdoors, fostering relaxation and entertainment.  This extraordinary home is perfect for multi-generational or income generating purposes. You'll find a collection of features that epitomize the pinnacle of luxury living. Discover a hidden room with a safe, providing both security and convenience for your valuables and personal belongings.  The interior showcases elegant brick floors that add a touch of rustic charm to the design aesthetic.
